OL,3,CSir Alex Ferguson leaving ambassador
OL,4,Crole as Man Utd tighten purse strings
OL,6,FSir Alex Ferguson will take a step
OL,7,Fback at Manchester United as he
OL,8,Frelinquishes a lucrative ambassador
OL,9,Frole he holds with the club. The role,
OL,10,Fworth a reported #2million-a-year will
OL,11,Fend as part of a club cost-cutting
OL,12,Fexercise.
OL,14,FSir Alex won 38 trophies at United
OL,15,Fduring a managerial reign spanning
OL,16,Fnearly 27 years, including 13 Premier
OL,17,FLeague titles and two European Cups.
OL,18,FFerguson is understood to have reached
OL,19,Fan amicable agreement with the club to
OL,20,Fcease his ambassador duties when the
OL,21,Fseason ends.
