OL,6,FFerguson turns 83 in December, and the
OL,7,Fambassador role is understood to be
OL,8,Fone of a number of time-consuming
OL,9,Fduties he is planning to give up. Club
OL,10,Fsources say there was no acrimony over
OL,11,Fthis matter, with Ratcliffe having met
OL,12,FFerguson face to face to say the club
OL,13,Fcould no longer sustain the ambassador
OL,14,Fpayments.
