OL,6,FThe Athletic reported Ferguson was
OL,7,Flisted as having received #2.16million
OL,8,Ffor his ambassador duties in United's
OL,9,F2014 accounts. Last month United
OL,10,Fposted losses of #113.2million for the
OL,11,Fyear ending June 30, 2024, but the
OL,12,Fclub insisted they are compliant with
OL,13,Fthe Premier League's profitability and
OL,14,Fsustainability rules (PSR) where
OL,15,Fbreaches are punishable by points
OL,16,Fdeductions.
